 ## -*- texinfo -*-
 ## @deftypefn  {Function File} {@var{cmap} =} colormap ()
 ## @deftypefnx {Function File} {@var{cmap} =} colormap (@var{map})
 ## @deftypefnx {Function File} {@var{cmap} =} colormap ("default")
